  31 Dec 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> ldapdns-2.05.ebuild:
  Change /bin/false to -1 in enewuser call.

  23 Aug 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> ldapdns-2.06.ebuild:
  Use -1 instead of /bin/false on enewuser call.

  31 Jul 2005; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> ldapdns-2.06.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

*ldapdns-2.06 (29 Jul 2005)

